Package wnlt

The package contains the classes of the Welsh Natural Language Toolkit (WNTL) which contains Tokenizer, Sentence Splitter, Part of Speech Tagger and Morphological Analyser (Lemmatiser)

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CYMRIE  
    HeppleCY
    Extends the Mark Hepple's POS tagger POSTagger class for the purposes of the Welsh Natural Language Toolkit WNLT.
    LexiconCY
    LexiconCY is an exact copy of the Hepple's POS Tagger Lexicon.java that permits HeppleCY class to use a Lexicon.
    WelshGazetteer  
    WelshNE  
    WelshPOSTagger
    This class is a wrapper for the WNLT class HeppleCY which extends the the Hepple's POS Tagger
    WelshSentenceSplitter
    This class extends the original SentenceSplitter class of ANNIE.
    WelshTokeniser
    This class extends the DefaultTokeniser class of ANNIE.

Package wnlt Description

The package contains the classes of the Welsh Natural Language Toolkit (WNTL) which contains Tokenizer, Sentence Splitter, Part of Speech Tagger and Morphological Analyser (Lemmatiser)
